    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically flawless: the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical intervention for this chassis. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock. The suspension retains factory-correct damping profiles with refreshed bushings throughout, ensuring the telepathic turn-in and lateral stability these cars are celebrated for. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, concours-ready specimen for the discerning collector.",
